# FunnyPenny — defense in depth.
#
# Personal data lives at ~/.funnypenny/ (outside this repo). These rules
# block the same filenames at the repo *root* in case someone fat-fingers
# a copy. Files under templates/ are explicitly preserved by the leading-
# slash anchoring below.

/soul.md
/memory.md
/tasks.md
/tasks-archive.md
/our_recipes.md
/my_voice.md
/user.md
/preferences.md
/contacts.md
/routines.md
.funnypenny/

# Editor / OS noise
.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
